flowchart TD
    Tick[POST /api/simulation/tick] --> Load[Load persisted state]
    Load --> Clock[Plan minute + 1\nand record unique clock event]
    Clock --> Complete[Complete due services\npatient-ID order]
    Complete --> Arrive[Register due arrivals\npatient-ID order]
    Arrive --> Eligible[Find registered, unfinished\npatients not active or queued]
    Eligible --> Services[Evaluate each incomplete\nrequired service]
    Services --> Project[Project work ahead + remaining\nvisit service time]
    Project --> Choose[Choose lowest projected whole-visit finish\ntie-break: service position, resource ID]
    Choose --> Queue[Place patient in one resource queue]
    Queue --> Order[Sort each queue\nurgent → normal → FIFO → patient ID]
    Order --> Start[Start head of each idle resource]
    Start --> Persist[Atomically persist resource state,\nqueues, timeline, events, and metrics]
    Persist --> Snapshot[GET /api/operations polling snapshot]

    classDef decision fill:#0F2032,stroke:#E5C04B,color:#E9F2F8
    class Project,Choose,Order decision
